originalText.text: A friend suggested that I try this place and I‚Äôm pleased to say that I did. I called and made a reservation but they do accept walk-ins. The business is on the second floor of 51 W 14th. It‚Äôs clean and quiet with low volume relaxing music playing throughout the space. There are approximately 10 rooms, each with a table. I could not hear anyone else. There are male and female therapists available. I had Andy as a therapist and he was very good. I definitely recommend.
